/lago-water-sports-centre","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0157","title":"Pine Trees Riding Centre ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/quinta do lago/fao0157_pine_trees_riding_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/quinta do lago/fao0157_pine_trees_riding_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Quinta Do Lago, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.06172,"longitude":-8.042482},"summary":"What better way to explore the salt pans and lagoons of Ria Formosa Park than on horseback? ","url":"/poi/algarve/pine-trees-riding-centre","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0151","title":"Quinta do Lago Beach","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0151_quinta_do_lago_bch_0416_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0151_quinta_do_lago_bch_0416_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Quinta Do Lago, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.02378,"longitude":-8.023356},"summary":"Known as the ‘jewel in the Algarve’s crown’, is the Quinto do Lago beach. ","url":"/poi/algarve/quinta-do-lago-beach","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0158","title":"Quinta do Lago North Golf Course ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve corrects/fao0158_quinta_do_lago_north_golf_course_0416_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve corrects/fao0158_quinta_do_lago_north_golf_course_0416_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Quinta Do Lago, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.0538,"longitude":-8.02705},"summary":"","url":"/poi/algarve/quinta-do-lago-north-golf-course","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0160","title":"San Lorenzo Golf Course","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve corrects/fao0160_san_lorenzo_golf_course_0416_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve corrects/fao0160_san_lorenzo_golf_course_0416_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Quinta Do Lago, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.03133,"longitude":-8.011487},"summary":"The San Lorenzo Golf Course can be forgiven for being a little well-worn as it seems everyone wants to check out its impressive views of the Ria Formosa Natural Park on the coast of Quinto do Lago. ","url":"/poi/algarve/san-lorenzo-golf-course","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0153","title":"The Shack ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0153_the_shack_0416_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0153_the_shack_0416_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Quinta Do Lago, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.03542,"longitude":-8.026526},"summary":"Decked out over the lake, The Shack in Quinta do Lago is a relaxed bar and a favourite with locals. ","url":"/poi/algarve/the-shack","category":"Eating And Drinking Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0244","title":"Ria Formosa","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0244_ria_formosa_530009166_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0244_ria_formosa_530009166_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01831,"longitude":-8.003279},"summary":"What better way to spend a winter break on the Algarve than with a spot of birdwatching? ","url":"/poi/algarve/ria-formosa","category":"Activities"},{"code":"","title":"Capela dos Ossos","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5005_capela_dos_ossos_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5005_capela_dos_ossos_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":38.56895,"longitude":-7.90827},"summary":"The Capela dos Ossos was built by a Franciscan monk in the 16th century and lined with the exhumed skeletons of hundreds of his peers as a meditation on mortality and eternity. ","url":"/poi/algarve/capela-dos-ossos","category":"Sights"},{"code":"","title":"Cathedral of Faro","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5006_cathedral_of_faro_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5006_cathedral_of_faro_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01331,"longitude":-7.934949},"summary":"Like many of Faro’s churches, its Cathedral was built on the site of a Moorish mosque. ","url":"/poi/algarve/cathedral-of-faro","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0246","title":"Christmas in Vila Real de Santo Antonio ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0246_vila_real_de_santo antonio_499539421_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0246_vila_real_de_santo antonio_499539421_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.19455,"longitude":-7.420902},"summary":"Want to experience the Algarve at its most authentic? ","url":"/poi/algarve/christmas-in-vila-real-de-santo-antonio","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0063","title":"Day trip to Lisbon","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0063_day_trip_lisbon_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0063_day_trip_lisbon_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01792,"longitude":-7.930755},"summary":"Europe’s second oldest city is perfect if you want the best of both worlds – city break and beach holiday. ","url":"/poi/algarve/day-trip-to-lisbon","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0064","title":"Day trip to Seville","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.10746,"longitude":-8.676301},"summary":"Stroll down the cobbled streets of the Santa Cruz quarter, making your way to the Alcazar Palace drinking in the scent of orange blossom, or climb the steps in the Giralda tower for the view across the city. ","url":"/poi/algarve/day-trip-to-seville","category":"Activities"},{"code":"","title":"Ilha da Culatra","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":36.98891,"longitude":-7.833611},"summary":"Grab your beach parasol and head to Ilha da Culatra for the day. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ilha-da-culatra","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0243","title":"Loulé Carnival","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1389,"longitude":-8.022492},"summary":"If you want to explore a lesser-known side of the Algarve, Loul&eacute; is a great place to start. ","url":"/poi/algarve/loule-carnival","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0144","title":"Mercado de Loulé","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1385422,"longitude":-8.02216148},"summary":"Discover Mercado de Loul&eacute;, an incredible covered market in this traditional town's heart. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-de-loule","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Mercado Municipal Market","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.02024,"longitude":-7.928533},"summary":"An impressive building in the heart of town, the Mercado Municipal de Faro is a lovely, cool place to come for a wander and to pick up fresh, local produce and people-watch. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-municipal-market","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0066","title":"Monchique Mountains","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.3111,"longitude":-8.594789},"summary":"Potter along the narrow cobbled streets enjoying a honey-soaked cake from one of the many cake shops or take in the restorative spa waters at Caldas de Monchique. ","url":"/poi/algarve/monchique-mountains","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia de Vale do Lobo","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.04789,"longitude":-8.064724},"summary":"Backed by red-tinged cliffs and carpeted in golden sand, Praia de Vale do Lobo is a real stunner. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-de-vale-do-lobo","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Ancao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.03276,"longitude":-8.038634},"summary":"Part of Ria Formosa Natural Park, Praia do Ancao is a long sandy beach backed by sand dunes and pine trees. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-ancao","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Garrao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.039608,"longitude":-8.050372},"summary":"Swit swoo, Praia do Garrao is real beauty! ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-garrao","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Praia do Tonel","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/algarve/gettyimages-175200196.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/algarve/gettyimages-175200196.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.0060158,"longitude":-8.947801},"summary":"This sweep of golden sand feels the full force of the Atlantic Ocean, making it one of the region&rsquo;s top surfing spots. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-tonel","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Regional Museum of the Algarve","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5041_regional_museum_of_the_algarve_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5041_regional_museum_of_the_algarve_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01617,"longitude":-7.931349},"summary":"The Regional Museum of the Algarve takes you back in time to how life was lived in the area many years ago. ","url":"/poi/algarve/regional-museum-of-the-algarve","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0067","title":"Sagres","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0067_sagres_187041329_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0067_sagres_187041329_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01469,"longitude":-8.941276},"summary":"If you prefer a more secluded getaway, you’ll love the laid-back vibe of Sagres where you can take in the rugged landscape of Europe’s most south-westerly point. ","url":"/poi/algarve/sagres","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0251","title":"Sao Bras","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0251_sao_bras_de_alportel_860247974_0918.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0251_sao_bras_de_alportel_860247974_0918.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1527519,"longitude":-7.889201},"summary":"Swing by the old-school village of S&atilde;o Br&aacute;s to discover the Algarve at its most authentic. ","url":"/poi/algarve/sao-bras","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0245","title":"Seven Hanging Valleys Walking trail ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0245_sete_vales_in_lagoa_699910450_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0245_sete_vales_in_lagoa_699910450_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08791,"longitude":-8.415715},"summary":"<p>Pinch-me panoramas are on the cards along this coastal cliff walk with its surf-splashed rock formations and secret coves. ","url":"/poi/algarve/seven-hanging-valleys-walking-trail","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0068","title":"Silves","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0068_silves_479077489_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0068_silves_479077489_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.18874,"longitude":-8.440215},"summary":"If you love old-world charm, you’ll love the former capital of the Algarve where you can lunch in cafés along the River Arade or take in the expansive views of the countryside from the red-bricked castle. ","url":"/poi/algarve/silves","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0059","title":"Slide & Splash Waterpark","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0059_slide_and_splash_waterpark_0414_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0059_slide_and_splash_waterpark_0414_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.13931,"longitude":-8.473315},"summary":"Water slides, spa treatments &ndash; yep, you'll find them all at Slide &amp; Splash! ","url":"/poi/algarve/slide-splash-waterpark","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Vale do Lobo Tennis Academy","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/female_tennis_player_1018988050_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/female_tennis_player_1018988050_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.0515366,"longitude":-8.05181},"summary":"One of the largest tennis facilities awaits in Vale do Lobo. ","url":"/poi/algarve/vale-do-lobo-tennis-academy","category":"Activities"}]}